<h2>ShareMyBag - Delivery Confirmation Code</h2>

<p>Hello <%= @recipient.name %>,</p>

<p>Your delivery confirmation code is:</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
  <span style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; padding: 15px 30px; background-color: #f0f0f0; border-radius: 8px; font-family: monospace;">
    <%= @code %>
  </span>
</div>

<p>This code is valid for <strong><%= @validity_minutes %> minutes</strong>.</p>

<p><strong>Important:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Share this code only with the traveler at the time of delivery</li>
  <li>Do not share this code by phone or message before delivery</li>
  <li>This code proves that you received your package</li>
</ul>

<p>If you did not request this code, please contact our support team immediately.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The ShareMyBag Team</p>
